            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Honesti Lautini dial<lb break="no" n="2"/><expan><abbr>epid</abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> ad <expan><abbr>aspritudine</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Honesti Lautini dia<lb break="no" n="2"/>misus ad <expan><abbr>veter</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cicatri</abbr><ex>ces</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Honesti Lautini <expan><abbr>dial</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="2"/>banum ad <expan><abbr>impet</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>lippit</abbr><ex>udinis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Honesti Lautini di<lb break="no" n="2"/><expan><abbr>agesam</abbr><ex>ias</ex></expan> ad <expan><abbr>suppurat</abbr><ex>iones</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Augenarztstempel; die Inschrift ist auf die vier Seiten des Stempels verteilt; Zeilenlinien für die Beschriftung.</p>
            </div>
